OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday looks mostly dry and very
OL,7,Fmild with some sunshine, especially in
OL,8,Fthe east. Cooling down thereafter and
OL,9,Fturning more unsettled with some rain
OL,10,Fand strong winds possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
